name: Pink Bible Study Notes Printable for traveler's notebook and Fauxdori, Faithdori, Bible journaling, Bible art journaling
description:
This is a digital file for a standard size fauxdori or travelers notebook.  The file will print on 8.5x11 paper and will need trimmed to size (2.75 bottom margin).  The file should be printed front and back, trimmed, and then stapled together in the center to form a booklet.

You are not purchasing a finished product.  You must download the file to print your own insert.

The Bible study planner is great for keeping track of your notes in personal or small group Bible studies.  It can be used if you are studying a book of the Bible, or if you are studying a separate book or devotional.  There is a box at the top to list the book and/or author.  On the left side of the page is a box titled "Big Idea." Below that is a box marked "Key Passages," a perfect place to write in a Bible verse or page number.  On the right side of the page is a Notes column.  And across the bottom is a white box for journaling inspiration.

Because I read my Bible and all other books on my Kindle, I needed a place to write my notes for Bible study where I could easily reference them.  And I'm always getting Bible journaling inspiration when I'm reading.  Now I have one place to keep them all.

If you would like the Bible Study Notes printable in a different color, please message me about a special order.
